    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... there is no \"own story\" where i belong. it's not just about taking a break, it's the fundamental feeling that i'm just wrong. like the world was built for a different species and i'm just a glitch in the system. even when i'm alone, i'm still tired. i'm just so tired of trying to figure out how to be a person.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
