      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It's really hard when you feel like you're an outsider in your own life. But remember, being different doesn't automatically mean you're a glitch. Maybe it's time to explore what makes you unique, and see how that can be a strength rather than a weakness. You don't have to fit into someone else's mold to find your place. Sometimes, the world needs that unique perspective.",
      "source": "target",
